# PHP Employee Management System

## Developed By

**Mohan Kalavalapalli**

## Project Description

This project is developed using Core PHP and MySQL as part of the PHP Developer System Task.

The application provides user authentication, role-based access, employee management, profile management, and identity file management.

## Technologies Used

* HTML5
* CSS3
* Bootstrap 5
* JavaScript
* jQuery
* AJAX
* JSON
* Core PHP
* MySQL

## Features

### Authentication

* User Login
* User Registration
* Role Based Access
* Logout

### User Management

* Add User
* Edit User
* Delete User
* User Approval
* AJAX User Listing

### Profile Management

* Update Profile
* Upload Profile Picture
* Upload Signature

### Employee Management

* Add Employee
* Edit Employee
* Delete Employee
* Employee Search
* AJAX Listing
* Pagination
* SweetAlert Notifications

### File Management

* Upload Identity Documents
* Aadhaar Card Upload
* PAN Card Upload
* Passport Upload
* Driving License Upload
* View Uploaded Files
* Download Files
* Delete Files

